<title>Qolymdy jaıamyn basymdy ıip РӘЖ262</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Qolymdy jaıamyn basymdy ıip,
 Júrekti daıyndap tizemdi búgip.
 Sóılesem Ózińmen jaqynsyń maǵan,
 Qupııa bar syrdy aıtamyn Saǵan.

[V2]
 Perishteńdi qoıyp meni saqtadyń,
 Senen artyq pana, Iem, tappadym.
 Sóılesem Ózińmen jaqynsyń maǵan,
 Qupııa bar syrdy aıtamyn Saǵan.

[V3]
 Kózimdi tigip aspanǵa qaraımyn,
 Alǵys aıtamyn, batańdy qalaımyn.
 Sóılesem Ózińmen, jaqynsyń maǵan,
 Qupııa bar syrdy aıtamyn Saǵan.</lyrics>
</song>